Package: laravel-deploy
Version: 1.0.0
Section: web
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: bash, curl, git, docker.io, docker-compose, openssh-client, ufw
Recommends: nginx, certbot, python3-certbot-nginx
Maintainer: Laravel Deploy Team <support@laravel-deploy.com>
Description: Laravel Sail Deployment Tool
 A comprehensive deployment tool for Laravel Sail applications
 on Ubuntu/DigitalOcean droplets. Provides interactive and
 automated deployment options with backup and rollback capabilities.
 .
 Features:
  - Interactive deployment wizard
  - Automated deployment scripts
  - Status monitoring and management
  - Backup and restore functionality
  - External database support
  - SSL certificate management
  - Firewall configuration
  - Health checks and monitoring
 .
 This tool simplifies Laravel application deployment
 by providing a unified interface for common deployment
 tasks and server management operations.
